{"tid":2510738,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"客家聯會高院門外抗議　促夏博義立即辭職","createTime":"2021-04-30T11:05:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T11:28:30.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b7681137294bc147183863d2a811a41b7b159f80","tid":2510738,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:05:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://dw-media.wenweipo.com/dams/wwpproduct/image/202104/30/608bce5ee4b03fc6f3b7018e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdw-media.wenweipo.com%2Fdams%2Fwwpproduct%2Fimage%2F202104%2F30%2F608bce5ee4b03fc6f3b7018e.jpg&h=c05ac8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港兩岸客家聯會表示，夏博義就香港法院對黎智英等人參與的非法集結案判決發表歪曲言論，是故意混淆視聽，偷換概念，刻意誤導公眾，煽動民怨，公然為違法者張目，為暴力者開脫，對執法者抹黑，對司法者施壓。案件經過香港法院公平公開審訊，又有被告主動認罪，不存在「冤屈」。他們批評夏博義對修例風波造成的暴力動亂視而不見，卻要為已認罪的人士吶喊，認為其完全喪失律師職業操守。<br />\n<br />\n他們表示，夏博義原為英國自由民主黨的黨員，是與外國有着緊密聯繫的反華政客，質疑其不會履行大律師公會此前聲明中所宣稱的維護特區法治、基本法及支持「一國兩制」。如果由夏博義繼續擔任主席，無疑是對大律師公會的最大諷刺，促請夏博義立即辭職。"},{"pid":"bc58dceb2203eb9aa69fb9126f0a8f5025b02b19","tid":2510738,"uid":125168,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:07:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad7f31cfbc78662daf7176c14a6d2fec12f3862","tid":2510738,"uid":13375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:07:43.000Z","msg":"群魔亂舞 咩狗屎垃圾會都出黎博表現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2b9c9a0473d308018f30dbd71cc07704d782cec","tid":2510738,"uid":19640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:09:47.000Z","msg":"幫手維穩都俾藍屍咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc3dcbd72ca6abfa7343e54b4b22669774db31b","tid":2510738,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cthks.com/20200717/20515\" data-sr-url=\"https